            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Hd1e108">Rubrica 4</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De incertitudine hore mortis et multiplicitate occasionis mortis</head>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-d1e114">
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>¶ De certitudine hore mortis et multi
        <lb ed="#V" n="52" break="no"/>plicitate occasionis mortis. Rubrica. 4.
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-d1e121">
        <lb ed="#V" n="53"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Rd1e118">SAlomon in ecclesiaste.
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>capitulo 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Qd1e127">Nescit 
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>homo finem suum: sed sicut pisces
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>capiuntur hamo: et sicut aues com
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>prehenduntur laqueo: sic capiuntur homi
        <lb ed="#V" n="58" break="no"/>nes in tempore malo cum eis ex templo su
        <lb ed="#V" n="59" break="no"/>peruenerit.</quote> 
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-d1e141">
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Rd1e141">Oratius in odis. libro 2. capitulo 6.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Qd1e145">Quis scit an adiiciam hodierne crastina vite
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>Tempora: dii superi</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-d1e154">
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Rd1e156">Seneca tragediarum in <sic>thebayde</sic>. capitulo i.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="64"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Qd1e158">Ubique mors est. Eripere vitam nemo non
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>homini potest. At nemo mortem: nulle ad
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>hanc aditus patent.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-d1e168"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Rd1e170">Idem epistolarum ad
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>lucillum. libro 4. epistola 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Qd1e170">Incertum est quo te mors
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>expectet. Itaque tu illam omni loco expecta.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-d1e178">
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Rd1e185">Idem declamationum. libro 7. capitulo i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Qd1e182">Multas
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>rerum natura mortis vias aperuit.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-d1e188">
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Rd1e197">Lucanus. libro 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Qd1e192">Mille modis intur leti mors
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>vna timeri est.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-d1e198">
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Rd1e209">Statius <sic>thebaydos</sic>. libro 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Qd1e202">Manet ingens
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>copia leti.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-d1e208">
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Rd1e221">Prosper sub vlti. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Qd1e212">Ferro: peste: fame:
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>vinculis: algore: calore.
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>Mille modis miseros mors rapit vna homines</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-d1e227">
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Rd1e236">Cato capitulo. 5. et finali.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Qd1e231">Tempora longa tibi noli promittere vite.
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>Quocunque ingrederis sequitur mors cor
        <lb ed="#V" n="81" break="no"/>poris vmbram.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-d1e248">
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Rd1e252">Isydorus solliloquiorum. libro i. capitulo 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10306-Qd1e254">Quan
        <lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>ti dum mori non existimant auferuntur. Quan
        <lb ed="#V" n="84" break="no"/>ti ad mortem subito rapiuntur.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
